# We keep the Docker image small by excluding most of docs/,
# but we explicitly include the few folders the full-stack image needs:
# - Finanzas legacy dashboard (static UI served at /finanzas)
# - Logistica prototype lib (imported by BmcLogisticaApp)
# - Admin Cotizaciones walkthrough data
docs/*
!docs/bmc-dashboard-modernization/dashboard
!docs/bmc-dashboard-modernization/logistica-carga-prototype/lib
!docs/walkthrough/admin-cot/source.json

*.md
!package.json
!package-lock.json
